---
name: Internationalization
alwaysApply: true
---
Always use t() from i18n for all user-visible texts.- Import: import { t } from '@/i18n'
- Use in components: <Text>{t('auth.login.title')}</Text>
- Use in errors: throw new Error(t('errors.invalidCredentials'))
- Add translations in i18n/locales/ when adding new texts
- Support both English (en) and Spanish (es)

Never hardcode user-facing strings. All visible text must be internationalized.